divs: Sighting DetailsWe were outside with binoculars to locate the Andromeda Galaxy and this cylindrical yellow-orange object passed over head. Object flew overhead in a straight steady silent path. Difficult to judge altitude - clear sky - maybe 10 seconds to cross over.
Summary: Unexplained object in night sky over Roseville, CA!
